"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;那个时候“北漂”这个词刚刚兴起。车水马龙的长安街，霓虹闪烁的街道，喧闹拥挤的地下铁，她第一次感受到大城市的气息，第一次看到了梦想的影子。</span></section><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;但是梦想在云端虚幻而美好，而现实却充满了苦涩的味道。每天挤在8个人10平米的地下室里，一天三顿都是泡面的日子，因为晚交了一天房租而被恶毒的房东把行李扔到了大街上，最疼爱的姥姥去世没有见到最后一面的悲伤和无助……在这些现实面前，她差一点<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box;\">把稚嫩的她压倒，但梦想让她不惧艰难。</span></span></section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></section></section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;\"><img style=\"max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle;\" class=\"\" src=\"http://hi.zan-xing.com/data/upload/ueditor/20160721/57909045ef1ad.jpg\"/></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"position: static; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">不过，“为了梦想谁不得吃点苦呢”她心里这么安慰自己，然后继续躲在麦当劳里啃着煎饼果子。终于，她的付出带来了回报。</span></section><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2001年的新丝路模特大赛，获得了北京赛区的20强，这是一个不俗的成绩，也为她带来了一些代言和工作的机会。</span></section><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,